long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Help you to identify Financial Risk (Accounting and Sustainabilities) from a report using the power of AI/Chat GPT. 

Financial Risk Analyzer: Analyse a document to detect risky part of the document and assigns the risk score through a DIY intuitive user interface to focus on what matters most for business. 
Allows businesses to focus on the mitigation of problems rather than detecting it. 
Bring the best of tech to work for business.
